description:
Perfectly located within walking distance of shops, beaches, cafes and both Bonbeach and Carrum Stations, this modern and spacious, second floor apartment gives you a prime Bayside investment or lifestyle at an affordable price.

Generous, open plan kitchen with bay views, dining and living with polished floorboards and split system heating and cooling gives you a comfortable and practical space to enjoy or entertain. Two spacious bedrooms with bay glimpses share a contemporary bathroom. The second floor positioning gives an extra layer of privacy and security, plus easy access to the communal rooftop terrace with expansive bay views - perfect for entertaining, unwinding, sunset drinks or just soaking up the stunning Port Phillip Bay sights and sounds.

Securely tenanted on a 12 month lease, this is a perfect investment for someone who understands the value of a premier location.
